charges.charge_description: 8:1324 (On or about 10/15/91 through 2/3/92 Harboring Illegal Aliens) IMMIGRATION LAWS, OTHER (1)

charges.charge_disposition: Probation of one (1) year on each count to run concurrently with the provision that the first 120 days are served in home detention. Fine of $1500 on each count payable within 30 days and a special assessment of $100.00 payable immediately. (1)

charges.charge_disposition: Probation of one (1) year on each count to run concurrently with the provision that the first 120 days are served in home detention. Fine of $1500 on each count payable within 30 days and a special assessment of $100.00 payable immediately. (2)
